Text: IT discounting week of June all We will be out of the office June through June On the mornings of the th and the th we will be airborne during the usual IT trading time As such we would like to sell for Tuesdays gas day on Friday June much like this past Memorial Day Weekend and for Fridays gas day on Wednesday June Fri June sell for Sat June through Tues June gas days Tues June sell for Wed June gas day Wed June sell for Thurs June and Fri June gas day Fri June back in the office sell for Sat June Mon June gas days business as usual While we are away you can beep us at If you call and leave a message please make it a DETAILED one because the voicemail automatically beeps us at the above number and we call in to listen to the messages Please dont leave a message and then beep us anyway you will just be delaying our response to you You can also try us directly at the hotel Please call either of us at the numbers below if you have any questions Robin Maria Robin Almond Contract Administrator Iroquois Gas Transmission System LP Maria Nemchek Customer Accounts Representative Iroquois Gas Transmission System LP
